      • getReferencedConstants

        public List getReferencedConstants()
        Returns a list of all constants refered to by this CycObject. For example, a CycConstantImpl will return a List with itself as the value, a nart will return a list of its functor and all the constants refered to by its arguments, a CycList will do a deep search for all constants, a symbol or variable will return the empty list.
        Specified by:
        getReferencedConstants in interface CycObject
        Overrides:
        getReferencedConstants in class DefaultCycObject
        Returns:
        a list of all constants refered to by this CycObject
